**Privacy Policy for Fill The Mug**

Effective Date: 25 Mar 25

At **Fill The Mug**, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our mobile application.

### 1. Information We Collect
We do **NOT** collect any personally identifiable information (PII) such as name, email, or contact details. However, we may collect non-personal data for improving the game experience, including:
- Device information (e.g., device model, operating system)
- Game usage data (e.g., session duration, gameplay performance)

### 2. How We Use the Information
The non-personal data collected is used to:
- Improve gameplay experience and app performance
- Fix bugs and enhance security

### 3. Advertising
Our app may display third-party ads that may collect limited, anonymized data to show relevant ads. We do not control the data collected by these advertisers. Please refer to their privacy policies for more details.

### 4. Data Sharing
We do **NOT** sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties. Non-personal data may be shared with analytics services to improve our app.

### 5. Data Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect the data collected. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.

### 6. Children's Privacy
Fill The Mug is intended for general audiences. We do not knowingly collect data from children under the age of 13. If we discover any such data, it will be promptly deleted.

### 7. Changes to This Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be posted with a revised "Effective Date."

### 8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

**Developer Name:** KM NIsha
**Email:** mail@dpmla.com  

By using Fill The Mug, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

